save animal.pl file in your folder
cd folder    (where .pl file exists)
then type in terminal

  swipl animal.pl                  // command
    
  welcome message should appear
then type

  go.                           // command
  
then type yes or no acc to question ending with dot(.)

  y.   // or n.                      // command
  
keep giving command y. or n. until true or false doesn't appear               // output
